items.name: Coffee Peets Coffee Major Dickason's Blend Coffee Pods

items.details: Rich, complex, full-bodied. Keurig brewed. For use in all Keurig K-cup brewers. Not for Keurig Vue brewing systems. Berkeley 1966. Our Promise: We believe there's only one way to roast coffee: with the precision of a craftsman who relies on his five senses - not a computer - to arrive at perfection. We believe coffee beans are at their peak the second they emerge from the roaster, so we quickly seal in the freshness to deliver you full flavor. We believe when we've done our job, you will experience something you've never tasted before - something uniquely rich and deep. The truth is, we don't believe in taking shortcuts and our approach to single cups has been no different. That's why Peet's can promise something you just can't get anywhere else: The uncompromised cup. Major Dickason's Blend - A Berkeley Original - 1969. Our first store on Vine Street. Loyal customer Key Dickason approaches Alfred Peet with his own blend. Mr. Peet tinkers. Before you know it, our all-time bestseller is born. Tasting Notes: Rich, complex, multi-layered; like a relationship with an old friend. 100% Arabica. Experience Peet's: Enjoy an expertly brewed cup at one of our cafes, or have the world's finest coffees delivered to your door. Peets.com. Talk to an Expert: Our experts are always ready to talk beans, brewing and the perfect cup. 100% recycled paperboard, minimum 35% post-consumer material. Printed in the USA.
items.directions: Not for Keurig® Vue® Brewing Systems.

items.name: Coffee Santa Cruz Organic Steve's Smooth French Coffee
items.display_name: Santa Cruz Organic Steve's Smooth French Coffee
items.details: Full body. Complex finish. Fair Trade certified. Quality coffee for quality life. For over 25 years, we at Santa Cruz Coffee Roasting Co. have been pouring our passion into roasting, blending, and brewing the finest 100% arabica coffees. Coffee is the seed of a fruit, the coffee cherry. Through the art and science of coffee roasting, we bring the delicate fruit essence of the coffee cherry to your cup. At Santa Cruz Coffee Roasting we are committed to the pursuit of sustainable coffee agriculture and equitable business relationships with our farming partners. Each day we carefully roast and artfully blend these special coffees and fresh pack them to preserve the subtlest flavors for your enjoyment. Certified Fair Trade organic. As you enjoy each sip of this certified Fair Trade organic coffee you are directly supporting the small scale coffee farmer's ability to grow the highest quality coffee, as well as supporting a better life for farming families through direct trade, fair prices, environmentally sound practices, and community development. Certified Fair Trade by Transfair USA. Certified organic by Quality Assurance International.
